=== CapitaSpring ===
CapitaSpring是由[[凯德集团|凯德集团]]和[[三菱地所|三菱地所]]共同开发的一座51层、高280m的大厦，耗资18.2亿[[新元|新元]]，正在位于[[新加坡中區|中央商业区]]的原金鞋停车场的地段建设。该楼将主要建有办公室和一间花园，以及[[雅诗阁|雅诗阁]]所负责的服务公寓、零售空间和小贩中心。该楼预计将于2021年完工。<ref>{{cite web|title=Golden Shoe Car Park to be redeveloped into one of tallest buildings in Raffles Place|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/business/golden-shoe-car-park-to-be-redeveloped-into-one-of-tallest-9027390|date=2017-07-13|publisher=[[亚洲新闻台|亚洲新闻台]] Channel NewsAsia|access-date=2018-01-19|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414113115/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/business/golden-shoe-car-park-to-be-redeveloped-into-one-of-tallest-9027390|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Tower going up at old Golden Shoe Car Park named CapitaSpring|url=http://www.tnp.sg/news/business/tower-going-old-golden-shoe-car-park-named-capitaspring|date=2018-04-13|work=The New Paper|access-date=2018-04-14|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128110528/https://www.tnp.sg/news/business/tower-going-old-golden-shoe-car-park-named-capitaspring|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== [[裕廊东#裕廊湖区|裕廊湖区]]（J.L.D.） ===
裕廊湖区的发展总蓝图于2017年8月25日公布。蓝图当中所指定的湖畔地区的发展方向将包括一间在裕廊东高铁站（[[吉隆坡－新加坡高速铁路|高铁计划]]已于2021年1月1日宣布取消）周围建造的商业中心，以及通过一条新运河延伸的第三座岛屿。这项计划预计将在二十年内完成。<ref>{{cite web|title=Jurong Lake District to create more than 100000 jobs, 20000 homes|url=https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/jurong-lake-district-to-create-more-than-100-000-jobs-20-000-9155708|date=25 August 2017|publisher=Channel NewsAsia|access-date=2018-01-19|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806230259/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/jurong-lake-district-to-create-more-than-100-000-jobs-20-000-9155708|dead-url=no}}</ref>

