=== [[登加|登加]] ===
登加是一个面积为700公顷，并位于新加坡西部的規劃區和未来的新市镇。它将设有五个开发区，每个开发区都有其独特性并设有“无车”市镇中心。新加坡第一家。登加的规划于2016年9月8日被首次发布，首批单元将于2018年开放申请。该新镇有潜能容纳多达42,000间住宅单位，其中70％以上的单位将分配给[[组屋#新加坡|公共住房]]，工程将耗时约二十年。<ref>{{cite web|title=A peek into Tengah, the next new HDB town the size of Bishan|url=https://www.todayonline.com/singapore/peek-tengah-next-new-hdb-town-size-bishan|date=8 September 2016|last1=Cheng|first1=Kenneth|website=Today|access-date=2019-04-28|archive-date=2019-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190921083726/https://www.todayonline.com/singapore/peek-tengah-next-new-hdb-town-size-bishan|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Tengah, the first HDB town since Punggol, to have forest fringe, car-free town centre|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/housing/tengah-the-first-hdb-town-since-punggol-to-have-forest-fringe-car-free-town-centre|accessdate=|author=|date=8-9-2016|format=|publisher=|language=|last1=Heng|first1=Janice|website=The Straits Times|access-date=6-11-2019|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204065528/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/housing/tengah-the-first-hdb-town-since-punggol-to-have-forest-fringe-car-free-town-centre|dead-url=no}}</ref>于2018年9月4日揭幕种植园将会是登加五区中的第一区，建造这一种植园的目的之一是要向1950年代居住在那里的农民致敬。<ref>{{cite web|title=First HDB flats in new Tengah town unveiled with community farms and gardens|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/first-housing-district-in-new-tengah-town-unveiled-with-emphasis-on-community-farming|date=4-9-2018|last1=Au-Yong|first1=Rachel|website=The Straits Times|access-date=6-11-2019|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109022443/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/first-housing-district-in-new-tengah-town-unveiled-with-emphasis-on-community-farming|dead-url=no}}</ref>首批单位已于2018年11月13日推出。<ref>{{cite web|title=HDB launches over 7,000 flats for sale, including first BTO project in Tengah|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/housing/hdb-launches-over-