=== 航空 ===

==== [[新加坡樟宜机场|新加坡樟宜机场]]第五航厦 ====
第五航厦预计将在2030年代末启用。[[新加坡樟宜机场|樟宜机场]]目前的可容纳约8200万人次，建好第五航厦之后机场预计每年将可承受1.5亿人次的客流量。<ref name="Straits Times Singapore">{{cite web|title=Decades of groundwork for T5 to take flight|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/transport/decades-of-groundwork-for-t5-to-take-flight|accessdate=|author=|date=3-12-2017|format=|work=Straits Times Singapore|publisher=|language=|access-date=21-9-2019|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111222141/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/transport/decades-of-groundwork-for-t5-to-take-flight|dead-url=no}}</ref>机场航站楼的面积将大于所有旧航站楼的总和。它将建在现有航厦东侧的填海造陆上。截至2020年，由于正在进行中的[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]，工程已停摆了两年。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Coronavirus: Changi Airport T5 construction to be 'paused' for at least 2 years, says Khaw|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/transport/coronavirus-changi-airport-t5-construction-to-be-paused-for-at-least-2-years|accessdate=|author=|date=2020-06-16|last=Toh|first=Ting Wei|format=|publisher=|language=en|access-date=2020-6-16|website=The Straits Times|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125110519/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/transport/coronavirus-changi-airport-t5-construction-to-be-paused-for-at-least-2-years|dead-url=no}}</ref>  在2022年5月，鑒於[[新加坡|新加坡]]實施與病毒共存的方針加上重新開放邊境以促進經濟復蘇，交通部長[[易華仁|易華仁]] 宣佈經過評估後，[[樟宜機場|樟宜機場]]第五搭客大廈的工程將於兩至三年内動工。

